).containsExactly(first, \"second\", \"third\");\n        assertThat(result).isNotSameAs(input);\n        assertThat(result.getClass()).isSameAs(input.getClass());\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 636, "output": 998, "cacheRead": 16384, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 18018, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777658646593, "responseId": "resp_0f83c24d4a9d8ad20169f4eb1700dc81a2a1d00b675c060a93"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_5FnyKUXESF488kzWGeZDUhV9|fc_0f83c24d4a9d8ad20169f4eb1e91d881a2a26707a3e2839274", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1770 bytes to tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/ArrayBuildersTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777658657203}]}
